      "updated": 1779061175151,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Functional reqs\n- Create account and login\n- CRD tweets\n- Follow other users\n- View a timeline of tweets from following\n- Like, reply and retweet\n- Search for tweets\n\nNon-functional reqs\n- Scale to 100M+ users -> high thorughput\n- Handle a high volume of tweets, likes and retweets\n- Highly available (99.999% uptime)\n- Security and privacy of user data\n- Low latency\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Functional reqs\n- Create account and login\n- CRD tweets\n- Follow other users\n- View a timeline of tweets from following\n- Like, reply and retweet\n- Search for tweets\n\nNon-functional reqs\n- Scale to 100M+ users -> high thorughput\n- Handle a high volume of tweets, likes and retweets\n- Highly available (99.999% uptime)\n- Security and privacy of user data\n- Low latency\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
