      "text": "Core Entities\n- User\n- Tweet Post\n\nAPI\nPOST /tweet\nGET /users/:userId/tweets/:tweetId\nGET /users/:userId/tweets\n\n\nData Flows\n- Tweet posting\n- User Following\n- Celebrity post\n- Celebrity follows\n- Celebrity page access\n- User page access",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Core Entities\n- User\n- Tweet Post\n\nAPI\nPOST /tweet\nGET /users/:userId/tweets/:tweetId\nGET /users/:userId/tweets\n\n\nData Flows\n- Tweet posting\n- User Following\n- Celebrity post\n- Celebrity follows\n- Celebrity page access\n- User page access",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
